                         IDSpaceManager idSpaceManager)

        Parameters:
        oboId - The OBO Id to convert.
        idSpaceManager - An IDSpaceManager which can be used to customise the IRI prefixes used in the conversion.
        Returns:
        The IRI of the converted Id.
